cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.CL 

This paper deals with logo detection and localization in real-world scene images using neural network components. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques for logo retrieval, which falls under the category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the paper uses deep learning techniques for image processing, which is related to cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also involves machine learning techniques for model training, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves natural language processing techniques for text recognition, which is related to cs.CL (Computation and Language).
